cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for multi-view people detection, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also makes use of deep learning algorithms, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with multi-media processing (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) in the context of multi-camera systems.
